extendedInfo.description: DataJog for Android allows you to send links, images, and text to your  devices from anywhere.If you like Chrome to Phone, you'll love DataJog.Add a new contact.  Add a new event.  Send a map.  Send text and URLs.  Add a note.  Start a phone call - Anywhere from the internet.Multiple devices supported - even across platforms. Plugins available for Google Chrome & Firefox.  Bookmarklet for browsers.- Create contacts and calendar entries from your desktop. Save time - no extra typing or sending emails with cut and paste. - Works with multiple devices - If you have two or more devices, they can receive the same information. - Links, Images, and Text - Send any information. No more typing long complicated website addresses. - Contacts and Calendar Entries - Add complete calendar and contact entries from your desktop. No need to start up device for information transfer. - Dial Outbound Call from your desktop=== Usage Examples === - Add contacts to multiple phones and devices from your desktop - Send all your team members the same information - Easily share data among friends by creating and sharing custom channels - Even if your device is somewhere else, you can still add data to it

reviews.title: Great tool
reviews.comment: I use(d) this already on webOS devices. It\'s very fast and has many functions. I like that I can send text from my phone to the desktop browser or another phone/tablet.
reviews.author: A Google User
